    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX 2150 - INSPECTION - CONNECTING RODS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CONNECTING RODS</title>
        <para>The BX-2150 connecting rod does not incorporate replaceable crankshaft journal bearing inserts and must be
            replaced if excessively worn. Clearance between the crankshaft journal and the connecting rod bearing must
            not be less than .001 inch (.025mm) or more than .0025 inches (.063mm).
        </para>
    </svcproc>
